feat: implement traffic lights and draw them on the screen
This commit adds the functionality to simulate traffic lights and display them on the screen. The traffic lights are currently static and do not have any user interaction. They are rendered based on their state and location. This implementation introduces the concept of traffic lights and checks the safety of vehicle movement based on the state of the traffic lights. The vehicles will now respect the traffic light signals and decelerate or stop when necessary.
